{
  "text": "Sequence database retrieval. The MS/MS spectra were used to interrogate the proteins of Vitis in the Uniport database (http://www.uniprot.org/) (downloaded April 2014, 56,310 sequences) using MASCOT software (http://www.matrixscience.com). The MASCOT parameters were as previously described [CITATION_1] . Peptide FDR \u2264 0.01 were generated for further analysis. We used Proteome Discoverer 1.4 (Thermo Scientific) for quantitative analysis with the following parameters: Protein Quantification: Use Only Unique Peptides, Experimental Bias: Normalize on Protein Median.",
